Author: Ethan Gruber
Date: June 2017

This folder contains scripts and documentation to extract monograms from TTF files into multiple SVG files.

Requirements: fontforge and inkscape

`sudo apt-get install fontforge inkscape`

1. Run 1.convert.sh on 1 or more TTF files (fontforge script)

    ./1.convert.sh Alabanda.ttf

2. Auto-crop only the useful area of the SVG (inkscape script)

    ./2.crop.sh


